sequenceDiagram
    participant Student
    participant ReactUI as EduPath App
    participant Netlify as Backend Proxy
    participant Gemini as Gemini AI API
    participant DB as Supabase DB

    Student->>ReactUI: Clicks "Generate Next Challenge"
    ReactUI->>DB: Fetch student's past performance
    DB-->>ReactUI: Returns completion stats & weak points
    
    ReactUI->>Netlify: Send context + generation request
    Note over Netlify: Proxy hides API Key
    
    Netlify->>Gemini: Prompt: "Generate intermediate JS lab focused on Arrays"
    Gemini-->>Netlify: Returns JSON (code, checks, description)
    Netlify-->>ReactUI: Serves generated lab data
    
    ReactUI->>Student: Displays new Lab Editor
    
    Student->>ReactUI: Submits Code
    ReactUI->>ReactUI: Runs sandboxed regex checks
    
    alt All Tests Pass
        ReactUI->>Student: Shows success + awards XP
        ReactUI->>DB: Saves generated lab completion
    else Tests Fail
        ReactUI->>Student: Shows error feedback
    end
